{
  "name": "TableStyleElement",
  "summary": "<p>表格样式为表格、数据透视表或切片器的一个或所有元素定义格式。例如，标题行是表格的元素。表格样式可以规定标题行的填充色为红色。</p>\n<p>表格中每个表格样式元素的格式设置可在适用于该元素的表格样式中指定。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除活动工作表上第一张列表中总计行样式元素的格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlGrandTotalRow).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第一张列表的行条纹1样式元素条带的大小。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlRowStripe1).<span class=\"hljs-property\">StripeSize</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表单个表格样式元素。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "<p>您可以将此属性与 OLE 自动化对象一起使用以返回该对象的应用程序。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果不与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象。如果与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表指定对象的创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Borders",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个代表表样式元素的边框的 <strong>Borders</strong> 集合。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将表格的上边框设置为红色实线的细边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> border = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Table Style 4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlWholeTable).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEdgeTop)\n    border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThin\n    border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlContinuous\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张列表中标题行样式元素的边框主题颜色是否为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlHeaderRow).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Borders",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回���个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Font",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Font</strong>对象，它代表指定对象的字体。 只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上第一张列表中第一列样式元素的字体加粗。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tableStyleElement = listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlFirstColumn)\n    tableStyleElement.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张列表的样式元素的字体样式是否为斜体。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlWholeTable).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontStyle</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Italic&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Font",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HasFormat",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回表样式元素是否具有应用到指定元素的格式设置。只读 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张列表中标题行样式元素是否具有格式设置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlHeaderRow).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasFormat</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第一张列表中总计行样式元素是否具有格式设置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlGrandTotalRow).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasFormat</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Interior",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Interior</strong>对象，该对象代表指定对象的内部。 只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上第一张列表的最后一列样式元素的内部设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlLastColumn).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第一张列表中标题行样式元素内部图案是否为纯色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlHeaderRow).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> == xlPatternSolid)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Interior",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "StripeSize",
      "summary": "<p>此属性不会应用于所有 <strong>TableStyleElement</strong> 对象。它只应用于 <strong>xlColumnStripe1</strong>、<strong>xlColumnStripe2</strong>、<strong>xlRowStripe1</strong> 和 <strong>xlRowStripe2</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置条带的大小。可读/写 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张列表的列条纹1样式元素条带的大小。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlColumnStripe1).<span class=\"hljs-property\">StripeSize</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上第一张列表的行条纹2样式元素条带的大小设置为2。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlRowStripe2).<span class=\"hljs-property\">StripeSize</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Clear",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>清除此元素的格式。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除活动工作表上第一张列表的样式元素的格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlWholeTable).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例清除第一张工作表上第一张列表中标题行样式元素的格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> listObj = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListObjects</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tableStyleElement = listObj.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyleElements</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlHeaderRow)\n    tableStyleElement.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
